## MODULE 2: AI MATURITY ASSESSMENT (300 words max)

Rate the AI integration on this 5-level maturity model:

| Level | Name | Description | Your Project? |
|-------|------|-------------|--------------|
| 1 | **Wrapper** | Just sends user input to an LLM and displays the response | |
| 2 | **Prompted** | Custom system prompts with structured output, but no learning | |
| 3 | **Contextual** | Uses user data (history, profile, scores) to personalize AI output | |
| 4 | **Adaptive** | AI behavior changes based on accumulated user data over time | |
| 5 | **Autonomous** | AI proactively takes actions, generates insights, and improves itself | |

**For each AI feature, assess:**

| Feature | Maturity Level | Prompt Quality (1-10) | Failure Handling | Value-Add Assessment | Upgrade Path |
|---------|---------------|----------------------|------------------|---------------------|-------------|
| [Feature 1] | [1-5] | [score] | [exists/missing] | [genuine/wrapper/gimmick] | [specific suggestion] |
| [Feature 2] | ... | ... | ... | ... | ... |

**Critical question:** If you removed the AI entirely and replaced it with a static flowchart/checklist, would the product still work 80% as well? If yes, the AI is decorative, not structural.

