## ANTI-PATTERNS

- ❌ Do NOT compare to "world-class products" without naming the specific product and specific feature
- ❌ Do NOT say "needs improvement" without specifying WHAT improvement with a code-level fix
- ❌ Do NOT suggest microservices, Kubernetes, or Redis for a hackathon project — focus on wins achievable in <8 hours
- ❌ Do NOT rate above 7/10 in any category unless it genuinely rivals production apps used by 100K+ users
- ❌ Do NOT suggest features without a feasibility assessment (effort + impact)
